<main>
  <div class="friend-room">
      <h2><%= friend.name %>의 방</h2>
      <img src="<%= friend.iconUrl %>" alt="<%= friend.name %>" class="friend-icon">
      <p>안녕하세요! 귀엽고 깜찍한 <%= friend.name %>의 방입니다!</p>
      <div class="buttons">
          <a href="/guestbook/friend/<%= friend.id %>/guestbooks" class="button">방명록 구경하기</a>
          <a href="/guestbook/friend/<%= friend.id %>/create" class="button">방명록 남기기</a>
      </div>
  </div>
</main>

<style>
  h2 {
    font-size: 45px;
    font-weight: bolder;
  }
  p{
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: bolder;
  }
  main {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
      padding-top: 0;
  }
  .friend-room {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 75px;
  }
  .friend-icon {
      width: 300px;
      height: 300px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      margin-bottom: 30px;
  }
  .buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 35px;
      margin-top: 30px;
  }
  .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 25px 35px;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 7px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 1.3em;
      font-weight: bolder;
  }
  .button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
  }
</style>
